16... Qf7 17. Ne5
{ Although Black is still not much worse, White starts to squeeze. The position is just very hard to play for Black. }
17... Qe6 18. f4
{ Rightly using his strength: the extra kingside pawn supports the pivotal point @@StartBracket@@e5@@EndBracket@@. }
