{ 1/2-1/2 @@StartBracket@@30@@EndBracket@@ Kopinits, A @@StartBracket@@2192@@EndBracket@@ - Borosova, Z @@StartBracket@@2231@@EndBracket@@ Olbia 2008 }
12. Nc4 { Black should stop White from taking on d6. } 12... Bxc4
{ but with a lot of regret. Our opponent is never eager to give up his best piece and his bishop pair. }
13. Qxc4 Ne7
{ And Black's sacrifice @@StartBracket@@of his strong e6-bishop@@EndBracket@@ has been in vain, given the next line: }
14. Ne6 { When Black's position is tumbling down. } 14... Rdg8 15. Nc5 Qe8 16.
Qe6+ { Knock, knock. } 16... Kb8 17. Rxd6 { This is just gallery play... }
17... cxd6 18. Qxd6+ Ka8 { Time to wrap up the game. } 19. Qc7
{ Black is lost. } *

