{ sidestepping the main line after 12.Nd4. As Black's position is a tough nut to crack, I'd suggest deviating from the main theory to confuse our opponent. }
12... Bxb3
{ This panicking move happened twice in practice is the only move played so far in this position. Black players well prepared will likely come up with improvements fighting for equality. }
