{ How beautiful chess can be, thank you computer! The queen is on her way to h5: how should Black parry the threat of Qh5? }
24... Nf8 25. Nxg7
{ Once again, computer, I thank you with all my heart being so inventive finding this superb idea. }
25... Rxg7 26. Qh5
{ Black is losing his rook because of the terrible mate threat on e8. } *

