11. Bxe7 Bxe7
{ If we are invited to gain a pawn, we should take this opportunity seriously. }
12. Qxg7 Bf6
{ The bishop's position on f6 cannot be envied. All White's queen retreating moves give him the much better position. }
13. Qg3
{ Black's attack has not gotten off the ground and neither will it. 1-0 @@StartBracket@@43@@EndBracket@@ Abdrakhmanova, S @@StartBracket@@2021@@EndBracket@@ - Braun, E Penza 2006 }
