{ Keeping an eye on g5, but prepares a queenside pawn rush, starting with b4. }
12... Qg6
{ 1-0 @@StartBracket@@22@@EndBracket@@ Socko, B @@StartBracket@@2643@@EndBracket@@ - Wrobel, M @@StartBracket@@1879@@EndBracket@@ Warsaw 2009 }
13. c4 { Would have held a gun to our opponent's head. } 13... c5 14. b4
{ Black cannot take because of c5, losing his bishop. His position is collapsing. }
