{ White reached a favorable ending, because of his better bishop than knight, and his higher influence in the center. 1-0 @@StartBracket@@50@@EndBracket@@ Guseinov, G @@StartBracket@@2664@@EndBracket@@ - Robson, R @@StartBracket@@2667@@EndBracket@@ chess.com INT 2019 }
