21... Kb7 22. d4 Qd6 23. Rc2
{ And this time c4-c5. White's attack is unbearable for Janowski. } 23... exd4
24. exd4 Nf4 25. c5 Nxd5 26. exd5 Qxd5 27. c6+ Kb8 28. cxd7 Qxd7 29. d5 Re8 30.
d6 cxd6 31. Qc6 *

