{ With Black's last move he took on d4. Was this a good decision? } 13. Nxd4
{ After this discovered attack, White gives up his Q&R, but gets back a QR&P after Nd4-e6-c7-a8. Noteworthy is that the knight cannot be trapped, as it can escape via b6. }
13... Bxe2 14. Nxe6
